{
  "texts": [
    "Future research should focus on expanding the dataset to include more linguistic variations and testing the system in more diverse realworld scenarios.",
    "Additionally, further research could explore the integration of semantic analysis tools to enhance the depth of error correction, particularly for contextual errors.",
    "This study introduced and evaluated a sophisticated automated error correction and feedback loop system integrated into the Chinese Large Language Model, Kimi.",
    "The research demonstrated significant improvements in the model's accuracy, precision, recall, and user satisfaction metrics compared to its baseline configuration.",
    "These enhancements have not only optimized Kimi's performance but also advanced its reliability and user interaction quality."
  ]
}